BOOTSTRAP_SERVER_LAST_OCTECT_IP    IN    PTR    bootstrap.{{ domain }}.
CONTROL_PLANE_0_LAST_OCTECT_IP    IN    PTR    master0.{{ domain }}.
COMPUTE_NODE_0_LAST_OCTECT_IP    IN    PTR    worker0.{{ domain }}.